            "title": "慈雲山慈正邨車路現鴿屍 內臟溢出疑遭車輛輾過",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3fa8c49bba056f2c89095323dd53b55b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051720040761611.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）傍晚6時許，慈雲山慈正邨正德樓對開馬路有2至3隻白鴿屍體，其中一隻更內臟溢出，狀甚恐怖，懷疑被人虐待。再懷疑有白鴿被虐至死。警方接報到場調查，不排除白鴿遭駛經的車輛撞倒及輾過，相信事件無可疑，大廈保安亦將鴿屍檢走，案件改列「動物屍體發現」處理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254410/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為慈雲山慈正邨正德樓對開馬路。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c954d33292e6893fb7d2ec64a07616ed/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_193725307.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為慈雲山慈正邨正德樓對開馬路。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254411/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場遺下一灘血迹及多條羽毛。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c2e7bec83b52598cab74111ed5cbdb9c/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_193544811.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-l